            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>At the Nepean Sportsplex, we take pride in being your premiere wedding reception venue in Ottawa. Our commitment to excellence ensures that your special day is nothing short of extraordinary. Here's what makes it the ideal choice for your reception:&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Versatile spaces</strong>: Our venue offers multiple rooms to accommodate both intimate gatherings and grand celebrations. Whether you’re planning a cozy affair or a lavish event, we’ve got you covered.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Seated dinners for&nbsp;400</strong>: Hosting a large wedding? No problem! We can comfortably accommodate up to 400 attendees for seated dinners. Your guests will enjoy the spacious and elegant surroundings.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Personalized decor</strong>: Infuse your wedding with your unique style and personality. Our rooms are a blank canvas waiting for your creative touch. From floral arrangements to lighting, make it truly yours.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Culinary excellence</strong>: Meet Tulips and Maple, our esteemed onsite caterer. Renowned for their culinary prowess, they’ll craft custom menus tailored to your preferences. Expect an unforgettable dining experience that delights the senses.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Guidance every step of the way</strong>: Our experienced team is here to assist you from start to finish. We understand that wedding planning can be overwhelming, so count on us to make it stress-free. Your happiness is our priority.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p>It’s a perfect union! By choosing the Nepean Sportsplex as your wedding venue, you’re creating a perfect union. Combine our elegant spaces with the exceptional services provided by Tulips and Maple, and your wedding day will be nothing short of magical.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="mailto:nepeansportsplex@ottawa.ca">Contact us by email</a> to arrange a tour and personal consultation.  </p>
