            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>The&nbsp;Nepean Sportsplex&nbsp;Curling Centre is the only public curling facility in the Ottawa area welcoming all levels of curlers. Join one of our many leagues or pay as you play during drop-in times.</p>
<h4>Amenities</h4>
<ul>
<li>Ten sheets of ice</li>
<li>Curling lessons and clinics</li>
<li>Curling leagues</li>
<li>Brooms available at no extra charge.</li>
<li>Lockers available but please bring your own lock.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Drop-in curling fees</h4>
<p><strong>Fees shown do not include HST. </strong>Applicable taxes will be added during the payment process.</p>
<ul>
<li>Adult: $5.56</li>
<li>Senior: $4.16</li>
<li>Youth: $4.16</li>
<li>Curling sheet: $55.04</li>
</ul>
<h4>Curling league&nbsp;</h4>
<ul>
<li>Beginner mixed league (ages 18+)&nbsp;</li>
<li><a href="mailto:SportsplexAthletics@ottawa.ca" target="_blank">SportsplexAthletics@ottawa.ca</a>&nbsp;for additional information.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Book a bonspiel (rental)</h4>
<ul>
